"I said, Nigga, get out of my house!"
Screams Rascon in response.
A blow is given.
And at the same time, everyone (at least all black actors) is being harassed.
Green laughs louder than anyone else.
"What is it?" asked Ascona.
He's worried and embarrassed.
Am I playing again?
