“Trump’s current and former staff say that Trump can react very sharply to negative press reports, especially containing dangerous leaks of information, and will not calm down until he finds out who was behind them.
That was the case in late February, when someone sent the president a printout of an article from GotNews.com, the website of provocateur Charles K. Johnson, in which the deputy chief of staff Katie Welsh was accused of being "behind a series of leaks" in Behemoth.
