The program of the second Skolkovo Jazz Science Festival, which will take place on August 26 in the innovation center "Skolkovo" has been announced.
Guests are expected to perform by leading jazz bands and soloists, scientific discussions, interactive venues and other musical-intellectual events.
As promised by the organizers, the site will become a territory of improvisation and a field for demonstrating new creative possibilities.
"Guests of the festival will be able to immerse themselves in the world of experimental media technologies and learn how innovation in science becomes a new tool for interaction with art", - described the focus of the forum by the vice president of the "Skolkovo" Foundation.
