Did PSG warn Barcelona of Neymar’s transition three years ago?
La Liga member may regret his interest in Marco Verratti
Paris Saint-Germain will not stop chasing Neymar after the club offered <0xC2><0xA3>189 million for his ransom, but did they warn Barcelona about the world record-setting raid that took place three years ago?
